registerActivityForAds

public static void registerActivityForAds(android.app.Activity activity,
                                          AdViewType adViewType)
Register an activity to receive ads. You must call this on your activity onResume method and you must unregister on your activity onPause method. It will keep receiving ads until the activity is unregistered with unregisterActivityForAds(Activity). It will show a AdView on the screen, accordingly with the AdViewType, which can be either AdViewType.BANNER_TOP or AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM.

Parameters:
activity - the activity that will show the advertisement
adViewType - the type of the advertisement. One of the following: AdViewType.BANNER_TOP , AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM

registerActivityForAds

public static void registerActivityForAds(android.app.Activity activity,
                                          AdViewType adViewType,
                                          OnBannerAdReceivedListener listener)
Register an activity to receive ads. You must call it on your activity onResume method and you must unregister it on your activity onPause method.
It will keep receiving ads until the activity is unregistered with unregisterActivityForAds(Activity). It will show a AdView on the screen, accordingly with the AdViewType, which can be either AdViewType.BANNER_TOP or AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM. You must call the BannerAdReceived#show() or BannerAdReceived#cancel() methods or the app won't allow others ads to be requested.

Parameters:
activity - the activity that will show the advertisement
adViewType - the type of the advertisement. One of the following: AdViewType.BANNER_TOP , AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM
listener - the interface for receiving the ads.

unregisterActivityForAds

public static void unregisterActivityForAds(android.app.Activity activity)
Unregister the current Activity registered in registerActivityForAds(Activity, AdViewType).

Parameters:
activity - The activity to unregister

showAd

public static void showAd(android.app.Activity activity,
                          AdViewType type)
Show a single advertisement for an activity. Automatically register and unregister the activity after the banner is shown. It will not unregister if the activity was previously registered in registerActivityForAds(Activity, AdViewType). It will show a single AdView on the screen, accordingly with the AdViewType, either AdViewType.BANNER_TOP or AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM.

Parameters:
activity - the activity that will show the advertisement
adViewType - the type of the advertisement. One of the following: AdViewType.BANNER_TOP , AdViewType.BANNER_BOTTOM
